node.text: We did it.  The longest solo femme Latin song Of All Time.  Telepatía is officially off the billboard charts.  Will we ever be back, only God knows.. but I’m so grateful for everything this song showed the world was possible from latinas, & to all the amazing people who helped keep her alive by showing love via interweb & radio.  All things ARE possible through God.  Thank you, thank you, thank u..
♡ celebrando sin miedo era on my youtube ♡ 4 months of telepatía music video
